Pierre-Loup Rajot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pierre-Loup_Rajot 0 Pierre-Loup Rajot (born 9 February 1958) is a French stage, television and film actor, director, producer and screenwriter. He is a 1985 César Award recipient for Most Promising Actor for his performance in the 1984 comedy film Souvenirs, Souvenirs.
